Class Movie

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.imdb.model.Movie

  • public class Movie
extends Object
    Movie object with fields.
    • This class has the 1 to many relation with Crew object.
    • All fields should be mapped to movie_metadata.csv.
    Author:
    widnu
